data.description:
Welcome to Riverstone, breathtaking mountain views await you! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is a perfect blend of beauty and functionality. Gated RV parking
Step through the glass front door, be greeted by a home that exudes pride of ownership. Too many upgrades to list. The interior boasts crown molding, Five-inch wood shutters adorn the windows, allowing you to control natural light and maintain a cozy ambiance.
The kitchen, adorned with beautiful backsplash tile and equipped with stainless steel appliances. The pantry, featuring a glass door, provides both practicality and aesthetic appeal. Contemporary ceiling fans in bedrooms, family room and patio.
3 car garage has custom cabinets, cameras and an epoxy floor, providing durability and a polished finish. 
Unwind in the in-ground 6-person hot tub or gather around the fire pit for cozy evenings with friends and family.
This home is a masterpiece of comfort and style, offering the perfect combination of modern and scenic beauty.
